Difference compared to http://code.google.com/p/annovention/
* ClasspathDiscoverer has been improved to properly scan all class loaders
  (based on http://code.google.com/p/reflections)
* Apache Common Log has been removed

== Using with SBT

val sonatypeSnapshot = "Sonatype Snapshot" at "https://oss.sonatype.org/content/repositories/snapshots"
val annovention = "tv.cntt" %% "annovention" % "1.0-SNAPSHOT"
